text: Regina Kleine-Kuhlmann (born 19 February 1959) is a German rower. She competed in the women's quadruple sculls event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:German female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of West Germany Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:People from Bramsche
